headline: Zelle owner taps Fiserv to jump-start mobile wallet
summary: Early Warnings Services is teaming up with Fiserv to quickly drive uptake for its new Paze digital wallet with merchants and credit card issuers outside of its owner banks. Paze partnered with Worldpay earlier this month to unlock a similar distribution channel.
